Package: ggplotStudioR
Type: Package
Title: Interactive MVP ggplot Editor with Shiny
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person(given = "Kana", family = "Assistant", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "assistant@example.com")
Author: Kana Assistant [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Kana Assistant <assistant@example.com>
Description: Provides a minimal interactive editor for ggplot objects using
    Shiny. Users can modify labels, themes, palettes, and point/line sizes,
    preview changes live, and export generated ggplot2 code.
